               <p>RADCLIFFE POND. I live at Chelsea. I was in <placeName id="t18270531-306-crimeloc1647">Pallmall</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270531-306-crimeloc1647" type="placeName" value="Pallmall"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270531-306-crimeloc1647" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-306-off1645 t18270531-306-crimeloc1647"></join> on the 4th of June in the evening, and felt a trifling touch at my coat pocket; immediately after the prisoner endeavoured to rush by me; I caught him with my left hand, felt in my pocket, and missed my box, and found him putting it up his sleeve.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
